<title>USA: IHOP Corp June same-store sales increase.</title>
<headline>IHOP Corp June same-store sales increase.</headline>
<dateline>GLENDALE, Calif. 1997-07-03</dateline>
<text>
<p>IHOP Corp said its same-store sales in June rose 3.2 percent over the same period in the prior year.</p>
<p>The company did not release raw figures for the period. It was not immediately available for comment.</p>
<p>IHOP develops, franchises and operates International House of Pancakes restaurants.</p>
<p>(-- New York Newsdesk 212-859-1610)</p>
